# Nedriva — Project Overview

## What This App Does

SaaS platform for AI-powered image and video enhancement.

- **Image**: Upscale, Enhance, Sharpen, Denoise, Restore, Face Enhance, Remove Background
- **Video**: Video Enhancement
- **API Business**: AI API for developers

Processing is **async** (jobs run on background queue); users pay via credits.

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Choice |
|-------|--------|
| Framework | Next.js 16 (App Router, React Server Components, React 19) |
| Language | TypeScript strict mode, no `any` |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS v4 — theme tokens in `src/styles/global.css` (no `tailwind.config.ts`) |
| UI Library | HeroUI v3 (CSS-first, compound pattern) + `@/components/ui/` wrappers |
| Icons | **Lucide React** — import directly, do not inline SVG |
| Auth | Clerk (user management + Billing embed on `/pricing`) |
| Database | Drizzle ORM + PostgreSQL (PGlite in local dev) |
| i18n | next-intl v4 (locales: `en`, `fr`) |
| Security | Arcjet (middleware bot protection) |
| Observability | Sentry + PostHog + LogTape |
| Validation | Zod + React Hook Form |
| Animation | Framer Motion |
| Testing | Vitest (unit/component) + Playwright (integration/E2E) + Storybook |

## Key Architecture

- All routes under `src/app/[locale]/`
- **Middleware**: `src/proxy.ts` (NOT `middleware.ts`)
- **Env vars**: MUST go through `src/libs/core/Env.ts` — never `process.env` directly
- **DB singleton**: `src/libs/core/DB.ts`
- All user-visible strings → `next-intl` translations (`src/locales/en.json`, `fr.json`)
- **Named exports only** (no default exports except Next.js pages/layouts)
- **`type` over `interface`**

## Design Tokens

All values live in `src/styles/global.css`. Use Tailwind `@theme` tokens — no raw hex in JSX.

| Role | Token | Tailwind |
|------|-------|----------|
| Background | `--color-page` (#000) | `bg-page` |
| Card / panel | `--color-surface`, `--color-elevated` | `bg-surface`, `bg-elevated` |
| Brand gold | `--color-brand`, `--color-brand-light` | `bg-brand`, `text-brand-light` |
| Text | `--color-foreground`, `--color-muted`, `--color-subtle` | `text-foreground`, `text-muted` |
| Glass panels | — | `glass` class (`backdrop-blur` + translucent fill + hairline border) |
| Hero glow | `--gradient-hero` | `style={{ background: 'var(--gradient-hero)' }}` |
| CTA fill | `--gradient-cta`, `--gradient-brand` | same |

Opacity / borders: `border-white/8`, `border-brand/25`, `bg-white/3`.

See `.cursor/rules/ui-design-system.mdc` for full design reference.

## Project Structure

```
src/
├── app/                     # App Router (all pages under [locale]/)
│   ├── [locale]/
│   │   ├── (auth)/         # sign-in, sign-up
│   │   ├── (marketing)/    # home, features, pricing, tools
│   │   ├── (workspace)/    # dashboard (authenticated)
│   │   └── api/           # Route handlers
├── components/
│   ├── ui/                 # HeroUI wrappers (Button, Switch, Slider, DropZone…)
│   ├── common/             # Marketing primitives (SectionHeader, Badge, Card…)
│   ├── layout/             # SiteHeader (glass), SiteFooter, BoostHeader
│   ├── pages/             # Route-specific sections
│   │   ├── home/
│   │   ├── bg-remover/
│   │   ├── video-enhancer/
│   │   └── boost/enhance-image/enhance-video/
│   ├── analytics/
│   └── providers/          # QueryClient, Toast, etc.
├── hooks/react-query/      # useQuery / useMutation hooks
├── libs/
│   ├── core/               # Env, DB, Logger
│   ├── i18n/               # next-intl config + routing helpers
│   ├── persistence/         # Server DB (users/, enhancer/)
│   ├── apis/               # Browser HTTP clients
│   └── react-query/        # QueryClient factory
├── types/                  # TypeScript types (domain, API)
├── models/                 # Zod schemas
├── constants/               # Feature flags, routes, query key factories
├── locales/                # i18n JSON (en, fr)
├── styles/global.css       # Tailwind v4 @theme + CSS vars
└── utils/                  # Pure helpers
```

## Route Groups

| Group | Pages | Auth |
|-------|-------|------|
| `(auth)` | sign-in, sign-up | public |
| `(marketing)` | home, features, pricing, bg-remover, video-enhancer | public |
| `(workspace)` | dashboard, enhance, history | authenticated |

## Domain Concepts

- **Job** — image/video task; status: `pending | processing | completed | failed`
- **Credit** — usage unit; cost depends on operation + output size
- **Operation** — `upscale`, `enhance`, `sharpen`, `denoise`, `restore`, `face_enhance`, `remove_bg`
- **User** — authenticated via Clerk; credit balance tracked in DB

## Commits

Conventional Commits: `type: summary`. Types: `feat|fix|docs|style|refactor|perf|test|build|ci|chore|revert`.
